abstract: >
  dNdScv_prep prepares a single, combined mutation table (SNVs + indels;
  columns: sampleID, chr, pos, ref, mut) from raw FASTQs or existing VCFs, suitable
  for downstream selection analysis with the R package dNdScv. The project focuses on
  being complementary to dNdScv, offering a container-ready, reproducible path to
  generate correctly formatted inputs at scale.
